- react-native-image-picker, react-native-chart-kit, react-native-svg
- react-native-markdown-display (chat + onboarding plan), @react-native-community/netinfo (offline)
- @supabase/supabase-js, axios, react-native-vector-icons/Ionicons
- @invertase/react-native-apple-authentication (Apple Sign-In)
- @react-native-google-signin/google-signin (Google Sign-In, patched via patch-package for iOS nonce support)
